      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk man, it feels way more targeted than just a \"glitch\" or \"privacy settings.\" every time i try to look into it, the logs are gone or the history is just wiped. it feels like they're cleaning up the trail. don't you think it's weird how these massive companies have the power to just... make data disappear without a trace if they wanted to? like, wouldn't it be easy for them to just \"glitch\" someone out of existence?",
